lass=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Clickable<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Container<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Anchor<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Label<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Clickable<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre><h2 id=\"anchor\">Anchor</h2>\n<p>Use a <code>&lt;Clickable.Anchor&gt;</code> to stretch a clickable <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> across the parent container.</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight language-svelte\" data-identifier=\"clickable-anchor\" data-mode=\"repl\" data-syntax=\"svelte\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        Badge<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        Button<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        Card<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        Clickable<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        Spacer<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        Text<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;